description: Front facing one bedroom, plus den/office at the Echelon Seaport is offered with private balcony, views, and (1) garage parking. An ideal floor plan with floor-to-ceiling glass windows facing east, private outdoor space, views spanning across Seaport District and Boston Harbor. Open concept kitchen with high-gloss white Italian cabinetry, integrated Thermador appliances, gas cooktop, quartz countertops and backsplash. Large bedroom, french closets, glass wall and views. Marble bathroom with walk-in shower. Interior plus room with closet, full laundry and white oak flooring throughout. The complex offers 24-hour Concierge, Valet Parking, Doormen, 1 indoor and 2 outdoor Pools, Hot Tub, Sky Lounge, Innovation Center, Fitness Facilities, Library, Private Dining and Wine Room, Outdoor Terraces equipped with gas grill stations and fire pits. An Iconic location offering fine dining, shopping, entertainment. Next to Downtown Boston, South Station, North End and all major transportation points.
